<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-relation-to">in relation to</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[正式用语] 关于；与…相比：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have a lot to say in relation to this affair. 
关于这件事，我有很多话要说。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Women’s earnings are still low in relation to men’s.
女性的收入相对于男性而言还是偏低。</p></div></div>